    {
      "author": "Adhityara Rizky",
      "authorUrl": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105739142710261405715?hl=id",
      "rating": 5,
      "text": "What a hidden gem in Bandung! I’ve been stayed in Japan for 2 years and this place remind me of a small coffee shop in Tokyo alley. The drink was delightful too, really love the chocolate even though I’m not a fans of sweet drink but this one is exceptional! The staff was very nice too, definitely will comeback again!",
      "textTranslated": "Sungguh permata tersembunyi di Bandung! Saya pernah tinggal di Jepang selama 2 tahun dan tempat ini mengingatkan saya pada kedai kopi kecil di gang Tokyo. Minumannya juga enak sekali, saya sangat menyukai cokelatnya meskipun saya bukan penggemar minuman manis, tapi yang ini luar biasa! Stafnya juga sangat ramah, pasti akan kembali lagi!",
      "date": "2023-05-22T17:30:45.224Z",
      "relativeDate": "2 tahun lalu",
      "likesCount": 0,
      "responseFromOwner": null,
